    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gather your energy into a single powerful ball of energy, ready to desimate any creatures daring to be in your way.</p><p>You make a single ranged ninjutsu attack against a creature within range, dealing 2d8 + your ninjutsu modifier force damage on a hit.</p><p>If you use this within 5 feet of a creature, this jutsu gains the Taijutsu keyword and you can instead make a single melee taijutsu attack, dealing your [Unarmed Damage] + 2d8 force damage on a hit.</p><p><strong>Wrathful Form:</strong> If you are currently benefitting from Wrathful Form, if you make a Ninjutsu attack you add your Unarmed Damage, if you make a Taijutsu attack you increase the die step of the jutsu by +2.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 2d6.</p>",
